measurement_metadata.description: Measurement of electromagnetic emissions from Quantum key distribution electronics. Contains measurement setup description and sha256 file hashes of measurement results.
measurement_metadata.comments: 2d measurement of the Rev1 module in a height of 1 cm. The orientation is relative to looking at the module from the top so that LMU logo is corrctly oriented. 0,0 is the bottom right corner, 0,1 means one step to the left. The probe is orientated in a 60 deg clockwise rotation from being parallel to the LMU logo for all positions measured.
